data.description: A Rare Gem with Stunning Valley Views as you drive up to the home, awaits the lucky buyer! Do you want a home, where you feel you are at a retreat, an entertainer's paradise, away from the hustle and bustle of the valley? Then stop, search no more, you have found the perfect home! Tucked away and nestled in the East Foothills, this home is a private oasis, secure on a cul de sac. The recommended access to the home is via McKee. This is an incredible single story, 3 bedroom, 2 bath home If a buyer would like to purchase the home as is, upgrade to their taste, do the remodel in due course of time, this home is their ideal home. The home is in an excellent condition to live in and make changes as you go along, to what you desire. It is a perfect blend of a home where you can live and make the changes, rather than someone else's taste, pay more, realize that this is not what you wanted, remodel again to your taste! Having said that, there are bids and proposals from contractors to make some upgrades. If the upgrades are made the new price will reflect the cost of the upgrades and will be in the market in 3 weeks.  The last pic is a proposed design idea by a contractor. Act now, or stay tuned for the new price, the choice is yours! Preemptive, Conventional and cash offers are welcome!
